{"tid":1534794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案 https://lih.kg/1530650","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:32:12.000Z","uid":108910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7161ab388353b6b0f21d7761b599c78c41cfb193","tid":1534794,"uid":108910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221fe1f124b8a548dafa42a19835fcefe82ba017","tid":1534794,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:20:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"644d38697f075bf4f3b8c27abb12f15c8960e3a6","tid":1534794,"uid":290156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed0892d01a8f9022f99f198c8b0ed708740a5fe2","tid":1534794,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"779c1239bb12c35200c77c438aed61326a3b889c","tid":1534794,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"[必看] 機場活動分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必看] 機場活動分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必看] 機場活動分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必看] 機場活動分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksEXTuP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksEXTuP.png&h=d9a8b7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiNeVHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiNeVHM.jpg&h=291d67fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLQ0Rf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLQ0Rf6.jpg&h=3eaacda5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phRGAHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphRGAHN.jpg&h=ec37db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xm2B82O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXm2B82O.jpg&h=f55b293f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"684af6f4fe906b45e1db26e0be22537466543107","tid":1534794,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"